 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By ROBERT MONROE 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   MOORPARK, Calif. _ Shares of Accelerated Networks lost half
their value Thursday, one day after the Moorpark-based
telecommunications equipment maker reported a loss greater than
analysts expected.
</P>
