   NUTTY-PROFESSOR _ ``Nutty Professor II'' is about how the Klumps
(all five of the grown-ups played by Eddie Murphy) are the engorged
American Family, made flagrantly obese lest you mistake them for
people who would fit comfortably within the confines of a sitcom.
And what lies beneath the geriatric sex talk, incendiary
flatulence, sagging breasts and earthquaking sprints to the buffet
spread is a family saga about home fires, Familial oneness and the
time-honored acquisition of a daughter-in-law. By WESLEY MORRIS.
