provocative images of nude children isn't the San Antonio company's
first brush with the issue. On May 5, Missouri Attorney General Jay
Nixon slapped the firm, which offers Web space for hire, with a
cease-and-desist order for hosting a Web site that contained
sexually explicit photos of girls. By ROY BRAGG.
