Dickel implored her to keep playing. Patterson was set on pursuing
a business career, and the accounting firm she was working for had
transferred her to the Bay Area. Now she is on New Zealand's final
Olympic Games roster of 12. By DWIGHT CHAPIN.
</P>
<P>
