for the
</P>
<P>
   high-visibility New York franchise in the Women's United Soccer
</P>
<P>
   Association inaugural season next year. By JERRY BRIGGS.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-COWBOYS _ Like 30 other NFL squads in training camp -- when
even teams like the Bengals prepare for the postseason -- Dallas
Cowboys owner Jerry Jones believes his team can win it all. How
good are the Cowboys, circa 2000? They'll begin finding out 7 p.m.
</P>
