   &UR; POLITICS (p) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   GOP-MILITARY (Undated) _ In a remarkable reversal in
presidential politics, a Republican team that avoided war is going
up against a Democratic candidate who didn't. But how many voters
will care? By Walter V. Robinson. 1500 words.
