<P>
   &UR; POST-SUMMIT TALK MORE CONDUCIVE TO GUNFIRE THAN NEGOTIATIONS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; CAMP-DAVID-AFTERMATH-ECONOMIST-800&AMP;add &LR;  &QL;
