<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CoxNet Cox News Service Sports budget
 &HT;    FOR Saturday, July 29, 2000
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   For questions, please call 404-526-5456
</P>
<P>
   OLYMPICS
</P>
<P>
   OLY-MENGYM _ Coverage of gymnastics trials at St. Louis, second
