like Willie Nelson, singing Christian songs. Some born-agains don't
like it because they think it's sacrilege for a dope smoker to sing
Amazing Grace. The show was the brainchild of John Peyton, whose
True Believer magazine, is being picked up for national
distribution. (Perkes, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
