<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-28 19:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6296 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-TEAMSTERS-MOVIE-BOS &LR;      07-28 0837
