<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-28 20:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6398 &Cx1f; tta-z
u f BC-ECON-REPORT-800&AMP;ADD-N     07-28 0961
