<HEADLINE>
VALDES TRADE COULD BE A COUP, WITH RIGHT ATTITUDE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Fixes fourth graph) 
By BOB KEISSER  
 Long Beach Press-Telegram  
<TEXT>
<P>
